  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large talavera plate over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the tamarind paste, makham paste, smoked paprika, and salt. stir to combine.",
    "add the short-grain rice and stir to coat the rice in the spice mixture.",
    "add the nuka pickle and bone broth. stir to combine.",
    "bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover with a lid.",
    "simmer for 20 minutes, or until the rice is cooked and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "remove the lid and fluff the rice with a fork. stir in the chopped parsley and lemon juice.",
    "serve hot and enjoy!"
